Clara's echymipera (Echymipera clara), ma ọ bụ Clara's spiny bandicoot ma ọ bụ *-egbugbere ọnụ ọcha bandicoot, bụ ụdị marsupial n'ezinụlọ Peramelidae
A na ahụ ya na West Papua, Indonesia na Papua New Guinea
Ebe obibi ya sitere n'okike bụ ọhịa kpọrọ nkụ nke subtropical ma ọ bụ okpomọkụ.
A na-achụ ya maka oriri mmadụ na New Guinea.
